  ('elementary-c5fb3965-moex-00102', 'elementary-c5fb3965', 'elementary-c5fb3965-moex-114-bdc7da1c', 'sub-elementary-c5fb3965-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關親等關聯資料申請與管理，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["親等關聯資料之申請，戶政事務所應於受理後7個工作日內准駁，駁回時應敘明理由", "親等關聯資料提供後，書面申請書等文件應保存10年", "電磁紀錄應保存20年", "親等關聯作業使用者身分，依業務性質分為管控稽核人員、查詢人員及資料維護人員"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:05+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f19cf4640384", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3b4f60409dd4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "503", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "戶籍法規大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "戶政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-c5fb3965-moex-00103', 'elementary-c5fb3965', 'elementary-c5fb3965-moex-114-bdc7da1c', 'sub-elementary-c5fb3965-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關除戶戶籍資料之敘述，下列何者正確？', '["同一戶長戶內曾居住該址之遷出國外人口戶籍資料", "同一戶長戶內曾居住該址之死亡人口戶籍資料", "戶長變更前戶籍資料", "同一戶長戶內廢止戶籍之人口戶籍資料"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:05+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f19cf4640384", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3b4f60409dd4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "503", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "戶籍法規大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "戶政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-c5fb3965-moex-00104', 'elementary-c5fb3965', 'elementary-c5fb3965-moex-114-bdc7da1c', 'sub-elementary-c5fb3965-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依戶籍法規定，檢察官於出具相驗屍體證明書後，未將該證明書送當事人戶籍地直轄市、縣（市）主管機 關者，應如何處置？', '["由其服務機關懲處", "處新臺幣3百元以上9百元以下罰鍰", "處新臺幣1千元以上3千元以下罰鍰", "處3年以下有期徒刑、拘役或科新臺幣30萬元以下罰金"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:05+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f19cf4640384", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3b4f60409dd4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "503", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "戶籍法規大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "戶政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
